Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.02,0:23:55.01,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\pos(992,488)}擺棋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨晚還真是有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 玩了一晚上遊戲呢
